{"word":"G4377 - προσφωνέω - prosphōnéō - pros-fo-neh'-o - Call unto","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προσφωνέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">prosphōnéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pros-fo-neh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Call unto</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அழை, வரவழை"},{"paragraph":"1. to call to; to address by calling"},{"paragraph":"2. to call to oneself, summon"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4314 - πρός - prós - pros/4314\">G4314</a> and <a href=\"#/G5455 - φωνέω - phōnéō - fo-neh'-o/5455\">G5455</a>; to <i>sound towards</i>, that is, <i>address</i>, <i>exclaim</i>, <i>summon:</i> - call unto, speak (un-) to.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}